-- Ukraine’s Akhmetov to Buy Stake in Ukrtelecom, Kommersant Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-09-28T07:26:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-28/ukraine-s-akhmetov-to-buy-stake-in-ukrtelecom-kommersant-says.html
SCM Holding, owned by Ukraine’s
richest man, Rinat Akhmetov, agreed with Epic Financial
Consulting Gesellschaft to acquire a stake in  VAT Ukrtelecom (UTLM) ,
 Kommersant-Ukraine  reported, citing an unidentified person
familiar with the deal.  SCM is aware of the possible sale of the Ukrtelecom stake
and cannot comment on “hypothetical deals,” said SCM spokesman
Anatoliy Yevtushenko in a phone interview with Bloomberg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
